  "text": "Physician approved manual segmentation was used as the gold standard reference. The spatial consistency between the automated segmentation and the manual reference segmentation was quantified using two metrics: the Dice similarity coefficient (DSC) [CITATION_1] and the Hausdorff distance (HD). [CITATION_2] Because the image segmentation was per- ",
